<!--
  Monochrome medication-bottle glyph for the medication-reminder notification.
  A capped pill bottle with a medical "+" reads unambiguously as medicine at
  status-bar size. The previous round scored tablet looked like the system
  do-not-disturb / no-entry symbol, and the diagonal capsule before it lost a
  half in the tint. The "+" is cut as a hole (evenOdd) so it stays visible
  after the system tints the silhouette solid white.
-->
